     * @notice setter function to determine wallet number THREE that will be receiving the funds
     * @param _walletThree : the address of the third wallet which will be receiving the tokens
     * @dev This function can only be called by the owner of the smart contract. Call transfer ownership if you wish to use a different wallet.
     */

